    - **`flex-wrap: wrap;`**: Allows the links to wrap onto the next line if the screen is too narrow, maintaining responsiveness.

2. **`.custom-link` Adjustments:**
    - **`flex: 1;`**: Enables each link to grow and fill the available space equally within the Flex container.
    - **`max-width: 300px;`**: Restricts the maximum width of each link to prevent them from becoming excessively wide on large screens.
    - **`text-align: center;`**: Centers the text within each link.
    - **`display: flex;`**, **`align-items: center;`**, **`justify-content: center;`**: Centers the content both vertically and horizontally within the link, ensuring uniform appearance.
    - **Maintained Existing Styles**: Preserves the existing background color, padding, border-radius, transitions, and font properties for consistency.

