  - **`translateX(-50%)`**: Moves the widget left by 50% of its own width, centering it horizontally.
  - **`translateY(-50%)`**: Moves the widget up by 50% of its own height, centering it vertically.

- **`width: 90%;`**: Ensures the widget occupies **90%** of the screen's width on mobile devices, providing ample padding from the edges for better aesthetics and readability.

